```{.r .cell-code}
shapiro.test(summary(mod1)$residuals)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```

	Shapiro-Wilk normality test

data:  summary(mod1)$residuals
W = 0.98867, p-value = 0.4293
```
